summary: The document is a classified routing and record sheet marked as SECRET, pertaining to the President John F. Kennedy Assassination Records Act of 1992. It outlines procedures for the handling and filing of classified materials and references intelligence gathering efforts involving South African political organizations, specifically the ANC and PAC, along with their European-based representatives. The document emphasizes the sensitivity and internal use only nature of the information contained within.
key_findings: Document is classified and marked as SECRET, indicating high sensitivity.
Related to the President John F. Kennedy Assassination Records Act of 1992.
Includes instructions for handling and filing classified documents.
References intelligence gathering activities involving South African political organizations and their European-based representatives.
